President Obama has announced his intent to nominate Freddy Balsera as a member of the United States Advisory Commission on Public Diplomacy and appoint Albert Gonzales as a member of the National Selective Service Appeal Board. Freddy Balsera is the Founder and Managing Partner of Balsera Communications, a public relations firm in Florida. Albert Gonzales is the National Commander of the American GI Forum and a retired employee of Quest Communications. Both individuals have extensive experience in their respective fields and have been recognized for their contributions.